headline: Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE:ICE) Enhances Loan Delivery with eRESI Partnership
summary: Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE:ICE) saw its stock price rise 5% over the last quarter. A key development during this period was the integration of eRESI Capital, LLC with ICE’s Encompass Investor Connect, streamlining Non-QM loan processes and enhancing market efficiency. Additionally, the company's collaboration with STOXX Ltd. on new climate indices and the launch of battery material futures expanded its market footprint. These initiatives likely added weight to its stock's upward move,...
